  <separatedmaterial id="aspace_ac1b116e9844a4d08c800e575414b99f">
    <head>SEPARATED MATERIAL</head>
<p>All of these posters can be found in collection <extref xlink:href="http://rmc.library.cornell.edu/EAD/htmldocs/RMA02746.html" xlink:show="new">#51-1-2746</extref>. Removed posters are listed below by the heading or first couple words of the poster. Simply search the <extref xlink:href="http://rmc.library.cornell.edu/EAD/htmldocs/RMA02746.html" xlink:show="new">51-1-2746</extref> guide for the titles found here.</p><p> AIDS Affects All, Cornell multilingual poster</p><p> AIDS is a problem for Hispanics, too. (English and Spanish)</p><p> Ayudando una persona que tiene SIDA</p><p> ¿Como se adquiere el SIDA?</p><p> El futuro esta en tus manos.</p><p> El licor, el crack y otras drogas te ponen en riesgo de contraer el SIDA. (Spanish and English)</p><p> El dejo de inyectarse drogas</p><p> El SIDA no discrimina.</p><p> Getting High Doesn't Cause AIDS.</p><p> How much do your children know about AIDS?</p><p> How to Avoid AIDS: A Few Tips.</p><p> How Would You Deal With It If One Of You Got AIDS?</p><p> If You Are HIV Positive (GMHC poster, Spanish and English)</p><p> If You're Dabbling In Drugs</p><p> If Your Man Is Dabbling In Drugs</p><p> It might take more than motherwit to tell my children what to do about AIDS.</p><p> Most people think HIV is only a problem in big cities.</p><p> No Matter What Shape You're In, Anyone Can Get The AIDS Virus.</p><p> On the wrong track.</p><p> Papi, ponte el sombrero.</p><p> ¿Quien cuidara de tus seres querido si tu faltas?</p><p> Sharing Needles Can Get You More Than High.</p><p> She shows all the signs of having HIV.</p><p> Since I got HIV, all I want to do is tell women that love alone won't protect them.</p><p> There's a simple way to prevent AIDS.</p><p> Today, almost one million Americans are infected with HIV.</p><p> When I found out I had HIV at age 17, I learned that anyone can get it.</p><p> Why there's a connection between sexually transmitted disease and AIDS. (English and Spanish)</p><p> You Won't Get AIDS From A Bug Bite</p><p> You Won't Get AIDS From A Public Pool.</p><p> You Won't Get AIDS From Hide 'N' Seek</p><p> You Won't Get AIDS In A Restaurant</p>  </separatedmaterial>
